## Decisions and Action Items

* **`draft-ietf-rpp-requirements`**: Officially placed in a "parked" status until the rest of the core specifications are complete.
* **`draft-ietf-rpp-data-objects`**: The working group decided to remove the constraint requiring strict array ordering for partial updates. Instead, the JSON mapping will utilize value-based patching.
* **`draft-ietf-rpp-core`**: The working group decided to drop the HTTP header option for profile signaling and exclusively support the media type option.

